{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d100be4583","title":"总政机关党委会、高院军事审判庭开除右派分子陈沂的党籍和军籍","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c426e05e30","index":0,"year":1958,"month":3,"day":29,"articleId":"d100be4583"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8b0109645b","type":"title","text":"总政机关党委会、高院军事审判庭开除右派分子陈沂的党籍和军籍","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d100be4583"},{"id":"d9ae2e87af","type":"paragraph","text":"本报讯总政治部机关党委会决定并已经总政治部和党中央批准，将党内右派分子陈沂开除出党。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d100be4583"},{"id":"d088fb9666","type":"paragraph","text":"又讯  中华人民共和国最高人民法院军事审判庭根据控告，认为右派分子陈沂反党反社会主义罪行严重，完受丧失革命军人应有的品德，已于３月６日判决，剥夺陈沂中国人民解放军少将军衔，并开除军籍。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d100be4583"},{"id":"bc5797efe5","type":"paragraph","text":" ——原载《人民日报》1958年3月29日。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d100be4583"}],"page":{"id":"0adc2416fb","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d100be4583","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}